scene.message:
Yukino: Are you okay, Ms.{nl}
Saeko? You must've been cold.{nl}
Any injuries?{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Thank you,{nl}
I'm fine.{waitkey}{nl}
More importantly,{wait_fr:30} where's{nl}
Tomomi?{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Tomomi is...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
the spirit that possessed{nl}
the mask.{waitkey}One of the students the Snow{nl}
Queen entranced.{waitkey}And...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
my best friend from my{nl}
drama club days.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: So...{wait_fr:30} so the Snow{nl}
Queen who possessed Ms. Saeko{nl}
was Ms. Saeko's best friend...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: So that's why the Queen{nl}
called you{wait_fr:30} "Saeko"{wait_fr:30}...{waitkey}{clearbox}But why would a best friend{nl}
possess you, I wonder?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hm.{waitkey}{nl}
No wonder she addressed you{nl}
so familiarly.{waitkey}{clearbox}But why would a best friend{nl}
try to make you a sacrifice...{waitkey}{ret}
